  ('dietitian-moex-09188', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者為細菌和植物細胞合成苯丙胺酸（phenylalanine）與酪胺酸（tyrosine）的先驅物質，並可以經代 謝變成對-胺基苯甲酸（p-aminobenzoic acid）或輔酶Q（coenzyme Q）？', '["苯丙酮酸（phenylpyruvate）", "對-羥基苯甲酸（p-hydroxybenzoic acid）", "鄰-胺基苯甲酸（anthranilic acid）", "分支酸（chorismic acid）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f0be3dbf80f4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7e47bc9a0ee3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097050", "c": "113", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技高普考醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試考試", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09189', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '去氧核糖核酸（DNA）的序列具有正常的變異（variation），大約每500核苷酸出現一個變異或是每一個 基因體（genome）出現107基因變異，即所謂的：', '["基因刪除（gene deletion）", "點突變（point mutation）", "多樣性（polymorphism）", "基因重組（gene rearrangement）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f0be3dbf80f4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7e47bc9a0ee3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097050", "c": "113", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技高普考醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試考試", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09190', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '5-氟尿嘧啶（5-fluorouracil, 5-FUra）與5-氟去氧核糖尿苷（5-fluorodeoxyuridine, 5-FdUrd）做為治癌藥物 的分子機轉為抑制下列那一種酵素？', '["核糖核苷酸還原酶（ribonucleotide reductase）", "拓樸異構酶（topoisomerase）", "二氫葉酸還原酶（dihydrofolate reductase）", "胸腺嘧啶核苷酸合成酶（thymidylate synthase）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f0be3dbf80f4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7e47bc9a0ee3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097050", "c": "113", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技高普考醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試考試", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09191', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '增強子（enhancer）可以增強基因的轉錄活性，其可以作用在距離可能有幾千個配對（base pairs）遠的啟 動子（promoter），具有下列何特性？', '["增強子序列只能在啟動子的上游（5''端）", "一個增強子只專一性的作用一個啟動子", "不論增強子序列的方向皆能作用", "增強能力大約只有十倍"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f0be3dbf80f4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7e47bc9a0ee3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097050", "c": "113", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技高普考醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試考試", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09192', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-097-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '勝格（Sanger）除了利用1-fluoro-2,4-dinitrobenzene定序蛋白質之胺基酸序列，他又運用下列何種化合物 進行DNA定序，並被廣用於人類基因體計畫？', '["2'',3''-二去氧核糖核苷三磷酸（2'',3''-dideoxyribonucleoside triphosphate）", "環狀核苷2'',3''-磷酸（cyclic nucleoside 2'',3''-phosphate）", "3, 6-二硝基鄰苯甲酸（3, 6-dinitrophthalic acid）", "2, 3-二苯基丙烯酸（2, 3-diphenylacrylic acid）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:52+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f0be3dbf80f4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7e47bc9a0ee3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097050", "c": "113", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技高普考醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、獸醫佐考試暨醫師分試考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
